{"tid":282573,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)恐龍戰隊 獨闖龍潭 新鐵甲威龍","createTime":"2017-06-13T13:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T17:30:41.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4bfdcd0563ef9cb665172297e47c0002d9032074","tid":282573,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:05:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=FHcrKzyvHfsKfw9ZqtVPbbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=2e11be12\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=FHcrKzyvHfsKfw9ZqtVPbbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b82ef38b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=FHcrKzyvHfsKfw9ZqtVPbbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d515e816\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/20160505222925_72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F05%2F20160505222925_72.jpg&h=a6dbd174&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d9/Commandoposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd9%2FCommandoposter.jpg&h=27a48d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/b/b1/Robocop_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fb%2Fb1%2FRobocop_poster.jpg&h=fad9dd19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.平凡學生變身戰士　力抗外星集團　肩負救世重任 眼見麗達女皇（伊莉莎伯班絲 飾）的外星人集團威脅毀滅世界，賢者宙當（拜仁鈞士頓 飾）選中5個高中生：金芭莉（粉紅戰士）、賽克（黑戰士）、比利（藍戰士）、崔莉（黃戰士）和傑森（紅戰士），授與能量變身器，讓他們可以瞬間換上裝甲擊退敵人。但大敵當前，他們必須先處理好自身問題，才可組成戰隊。最終，他們能否引發所有潛能，合力召喚出「超級戰鬥龍」對付終極怪物？<br />\n<br />\n2.約翰&middot;馬特里克斯（阿諾&middot;史瓦辛格飾）是三角洲部隊的一位退役上校，他得知自己在部隊中的上司富蘭克林&middot;科比少將以及小隊中的所有戰友都被一夥來歷不明的僱傭兵所殺。原來這夥人以前也是三角洲部隊成員，因為過於殘暴而被開除出隊伍後懷恨在心決心報復。他們接下來又偷襲了馬特里克斯的家，綁架了他的女兒簡妮<br />\n<br />\n3.以2028年的底特律為背景，2028年跨國企業Omni Corp已成為機器人科技發展的核心，他們超卓的表現更引領美國於世界各地的戰爭中取得勝利，然而由於對機器人沒有人類良知的意識和思維的顧慮，美國民眾和國會議員大多反對在本土部署機器警察和士兵；而接下來Omni Corp公司更希望能令這種科技更加普及化..<br />\n<br />\n9 20PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6ff5c3e7a8f9e5f824007308fb93b5a53b5448","tid":282573,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c151a2f6f01e886cb09227a20525ca422a2a2d04","tid":282573,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f395c5190004af21aaabc8a3c6efdcfeef0d948","tid":282573,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T13:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac17b2ae6909bc0e0f027166ecd0a8ba7a79368","tid":282573,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f